1:21:11.283 --> 1:21:13.869
♪ You can spot a hawk a mile away ♪

1:21:14.369 --> 1:21:16.663
♪ Cursing all those old blue jays ♪

1:21:16.913 --> 1:21:19.040
♪ But every time I turn around ♪

1:21:19.124 --> 1:21:19.958
No.

1:21:20.041 --> 1:21:22.794
♪ And have given up for good ♪

