[Naomi] Logan!

1:21:29.342 --> 1:21:30.844
[grunting]

1:21:36.600 --> 1:21:37.726
[panting]

1:21:43.857 --> 1:21:44.900
Mom! Mom?

1:21:45.650 --> 1:21:46.610
[Naomi] Help!

1:21:55.035 --> 1:21:57.037
[Naomi] Logan!

1:22:07.297 --> 1:22:08.173
[grunts]

1:22:17.724 --> 1:22:18.767
[clanging]

1:22:24.606 --> 1:22:25.815
[ragged breathing]

1:23:18.159 --> 1:23:19.744
[Naomi cries]

1:23:50.900 --> 1:23:51.860
Mom?

1:24:11.921 --> 1:24:13.256
Logan! [yelps]

1:24:18.970 --> 1:24:19.804
[Logan gasps]

1:24:21.306 --> 1:24:22.140
[Naomi gurgles]

1:24:22.599 --> 1:24:23.725
Mom?

1:24:24.726 --> 1:24:25.560
Mom?

1:24:26.811 --> 1:24:27.645
No.

1:24:27.729 --> 1:24:29.230
[Naomi gasping]

1:24:31.441 --> 1:24:33.526
Run! Run!

1:24:33.610 --> 1:24:34.652
No! Mom!

1:24:34.736 --> 1:24:35.653
[Naomi falls]

1:24:37.614 --> 1:24:38.490
[gasps]

1:24:44.746 --> 1:24:46.039
[screaming]

1:25:03.848 --> 1:25:05.308
[screaming]

1:25:12.065 --> 1:25:13.066
[muffled groaning]

1:25:25.495 --> 1:25:26.329
No!

