-No!
-Now run!

1:26:03.575 --> 1:26:04.450
Help!

1:26:06.661 --> 1:26:08.329
Somebody help me!

1:26:10.165 --> 1:26:10.999
Aah!

1:26:31.686 --> 1:26:32.896
[panting]

1:26:36.524 --> 1:26:37.483
[branches snapping]

1:26:43.156 --> 1:26:44.532
[footsteps approaching]

1:27:41.464 --> 1:27:42.715
[gasping]

1:27:53.851 --> 1:27:54.686
[coughs]

1:28:47.071 --> 1:28:49.240
[screams]

1:28:50.658 --> 1:28:51.492
Please!

1:28:52.201 --> 1:28:53.536
Don't hurt me! Please.

1:28:54.078 --> 1:28:56.789
No! Don't hurt me! No!

1:28:56.873 --> 1:28:58.166
No!

1:28:58.249 --> 1:28:59.292
[screaming]

